title: BrevisRefero and BioTalent
content: In September of 2021 I will be the faculty supervisor for a BioTalent Canada grant between BrevisRefero and Humber College.

title: LiveCode Visual Code Studio Extension
content:
Programmed a Visual Studio Code extension called LiveCode to provide students with a copyable, easy to read, plain text, real-time version of my code I stream. As I code using Visual Studio Code my code is made available to students using the LiveCode Viewer.

The LiveCode extension is available in the Visual Studio Code Marketplace.

title: BrevisRefero and Mitacs
content:
In September of 2020 I will be supervising a cluster of students from Humber College and Willis College through a six month Mitacs research project. Students will come from the Web Design and Interactive Media, User Experience, and Project Management programs from Humber College; and the Cyber Security Analyst from the Willis College.

In partnership with BrevisRefero students will contribute to the development and maintenance of their online RFP platform to connect BioPharma Innovator companies with a global network of Service Providers that offer biologics development and manufacturing services.

Mitacs helps connect industry and post-secondary institutions, driving collaborations to develop projects which solve business challenges, and develop Canadian innovation capacity.

title: A Case Study of Pedagogical Approaches Teaching Code in Postsecondary Education
